5658bb77da4ca7b9e92c0296f8719a","tid":2347814,"uid":20291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"真係好似班小丑，都唔知做物撚嘢"},{"pid":"88cf6f737cffee956d1b8278f2d758f24e5d9f54","tid":2347814,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"成條彌敦道由太子到尖咀都係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11abe47d30b01a904c3bdeef8d30f47e34db1671","tid":2347814,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ff4540b266db57df8447e5c8102d8fb8c8ab98","tid":2347814,"uid":361751,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7GEBLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7GEBLP.jpg&h=a8114d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n短袖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"da66e68a286a60139d585033459904b956b86e66","tid":2347814,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"死柒頭畜犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}